        ty:Your local dealers should have these superb products.
        ty:If they don't, ask them why, and then feel free
        ty:to call us.  Working hours are 9-6, and our phone is
        ty:(409)-846-1311 .
        ty:
        done
      else
        ty:There's no computer here!
      endif
      done
     else
      ty:You don't have a disk!
     endif
     done
    poend
    ty:Insert it where!?!
    done

BACKGROUND

